Class SuggestionFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • com.edit.reach.fragments.SuggestionFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public class SuggestionFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
    When a button has been clicked in the controlfragment this fragment gives the user a way to choose a milestone. The user can skip to get next milestone or add the milestone to the route.
